LARDD 1
TITLE LardOS Driver Catalog Manifest
TEXT Branch: drivers
TEXT Purpose: keep optional drivers in categorized folders so users can install what they need.
SECTION Bundles
ITEM bundles/core-drivers/core-drivers.rxr -> installs drv-rtl8139.drfl, drv-piix3ide.drfl, and driverctl.rxe.
SECTION Network
ITEM network/rtl8139/rtl8139.rxr -> Realtek RTL8139 PCI NIC descriptor bundle.
ITEM network/rtl8139/drv-rtl8139.drfl -> raw DRFL descriptor for PCI 10EC:8139, driver rtl8139.
SECTION Storage
ITEM storage/piix3ide/piix3ide.rxr -> Intel PIIX3 IDE/ATA-PIO descriptor bundle.
ITEM storage/piix3ide/drv-piix3ide.drfl -> raw DRFL descriptor for PCI 8086:7010, driver ata-pio.
SECTION Empty Categories
ITEM display -> reserved for framebuffer and graphics descriptors.
ITEM input -> reserved for keyboard, mouse, and pointer descriptors.
ITEM usb -> reserved for USB controller and device descriptors.
ITEM vm -> reserved for virtual-machine helper descriptors.
SECTION Commands
ITEM rxr verify file.rxr
ITEM rxr install file.rxr
ITEM drivers reload
ITEM drivers load file.drfl
ITEM drivers
END
